      "width": 400.4394226074219,
      "height": 100.00000000000001,
      "text": "Sources:\n\n· lovesac-solution-design.docx — §3.3 backends, §4.4 BOM, Open Q6/Q7\n\n· lovesac-compatibility-rules.docx — AI-derived rules from Product File\n\n· Lovesac_Sactional_Builder_Guide.docx — adjacency rules, ThreeKit config\n\n· New Product Hierarchy Review.pdf — 3 competing hierarchy proposals\n\n· Lovesac Target Architecture.jpg — Celigo, Manhattan, Salesforce Retail Cloud\n\n· Requirements Definition.docx — contracted scope\n\nPhase 1 target: June 30, 2026  |  DX Engine = free POC for 1 year",
      "originalText": "Sources:\n\n· lovesac-solution-design.docx — §3.3 backends, §4.4 BOM, Open Q6/Q7\n\n· lovesac-compatibility-rules.docx — AI-derived rules from Product File\n\n· Lovesac_Sactional_Builder_Guide.docx — adjacency rules, ThreeKit config\n\n· New Product Hierarchy Review.pdf — 3 competing hierarchy proposals\n\n· Lovesac Target Architecture.jpg — Celigo, Manhattan, Salesforce Retail Cloud\n\n· Requirements Definition.docx — contracted scope\n\nPhase 1 target: June 30, 2026  |  DX Engine = free POC for 1 year",
